 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Senior Functional Test Analyst Capgemini 8,255 reviews Richmond, VA Capgemini 8,255 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Contract Full Job Description Duration :6+Months 
Responsibilities : 
Must have Skills: Functional Testing 
Nice to have Skills: Test Automation (TOSCA) 
Creating Test Plan for the projects. 
Understanding the Requirements after discussion with customer stakeholders. 
Documenting Test Scenarios and getting this reviewed with the customer stakeholders. 
Documenting Test Scripts and getting this reviewed by the customer stakeholders. 
Coordinating with the offshore team and share the Functional knowledge to the team. 
Review the artifacts shared by the offshore team before sharing it with the customers. 
Provide testing estimates to the customer. 
Responsible person for meeting project deadlines and escalating issue to the customers and provide solutions. 
Conduct weekly status review with the customer stakeholders and discuss on the project progress and issues. 
Share daily status updates on testing progress to the customer management team. 
Document and share UAT Approval Document after testing completion for different projects. 
Be part of all Agile ceremonies and lead the team. 
